​m up


Starts all your media apps in the background.


​m gpu


Live monitor for your GTX 750 temperature and usage.


​m ps


Shows exactly which apps are running and their ports.


​m reset


The "Nuclear" option: wipes cache and restarts the entire stack.


​m mount


Refreshes and remounts your Expansion drive "Vault."


​m status


Dashboard view of storage, GPU, and container health.


​Quick File Paths


​Blueprint: ~/mercury/docker-compose.yml


​Vault: /media/linux/Expansion


​Configs: ~/mercury/config/

